{"id": "1185614007474868385", "channel_id": "1185614007474868385", "type": 0, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "1、目前制作组有考虑添加一个命轮配置保存与命契配置一键保存更换功能嘛（另外SSR命轮不能同时携带两张这样设计虽说维持了部分角色强度\n但很影响SSR命轮抽取意愿耶，后续会考虑更改这命轮携带这方面的限制吗）\n2、关于常驻命轮唤醒池是否可以添加例如角色活动唤醒池的保底机制（120指定命轮）\n常驻角色唤醒池同理（120指定唤醒）\n3、当前游戏中貌似不存在游戏周常活动，以及运营方日后会有开放更多活动的筹备嘛\n4、目前游戏内部分界域角色强度明显不如其他界域哎（日后会出同界域UP角色进行强度补正嘛）\n还有up角色日程可以放在游戏公告通知嘛\n部分大陆网友也挺辛苦的喂\n5、制作组目前有考虑开发新玩法吗\n例如杀戮尖塔\n无尽爬塔模式\n亦或是暗黑地牢的理智值机制（非常契合你游的世界观）\n6、游戏左下方网络显示延迟是否可以添加关闭显示功能（非常影响游戏观感体验）\n7、游戏wiki上方置顶宣传。非常败路人缘的喂，运营可以把它下了嘛（不清楚是不是官方有在入驻，总之就是非常败路人缘）\n最后希望制作组有人能看见", "timestamp": "2023-12-16T16:06:47.025000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1185614007814586460", "filename": "0F5AF68D07CF712FF35BDC9EC74139AD.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 24352, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1185614007474868385/1185614007814586460/0F5AF68D07CF712FF35BDC9EC74139AD.jpg?ex=69cc99d7&is=69cb4857&hm=9a8a8cbd3cc05fe3ad2bf2e0e8141e8025d166bfbcd5ec12e1c0e1951de3dfcd&"}, {"id": "1185614008062058666", "filename": "AE6D32D91682898ACB6D4432BFEEC979.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 39618, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1185614007474868385/1185614008062058666/AE6D32D91682898ACB6D4432BFEEC979.jpg?ex=69cc99d7&is=69cb4857&hm=f5e94c512b8ab5e7d0f3d73003bc04b74d92a08dc67126f1b197db218fbbb57d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1185614007474868385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」游戏建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1185475930731331635", "channel_id": "1185475930731331635", "type": 0, "author_id": "1115571459599908955", "author_name": "zero9016", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi Everyone, \nSorry i can't write in Chinese and i didn't want to use google translate  as sometimes the translation is wrong\nI'm very happy with the developers decisions and i think this game is going to be a huge success if it lunches globally, however i wanted to give my feedback to the developers regards the pvp system \n\n Paid battle pass card that has effect on the gameplay should not be allowed in pvp as it gives advantage to the people that spend money on the game over the free to play players\n and that's consider to be a pay to win and unacceptable for people like me who doesn't spend money on games", "timestamp": "2023-12-16T06:58:06.964000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😋", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [{"id": "1185475931318521918", "filename": "Screenshot_20231216_130107__Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 125857, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1185475930731331635/1185475931318521918/Screenshot_20231216_130107__Morimens.jpg?ex=69ccc1ff&is=69cb707f&hm=b76b394adf59a1e31db541d44bdb3ad33ccd4ab133360192e0d6a961f96d81ae&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1185475930731331635", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」PVP 付费通关", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
